<li>Words can't express how sorry I am. I will do everything I can to make things right.</li>
<li>My heart aches with regret for the hurt I've caused.  I cherish our family and desperately want to heal this rift.</li>
<li>I am truly sorry for my hurtful words/actions. I promise to do better.</li>
<li>Please accept my sincerest apologies. I understand my mistake deeply and will strive for improvement.</li>
<li>I know an apology isn't enough, but please know how remorseful I am.</li>
<li>Forgive me, please.  My intentions were never to cause you harm.</li>
<li>I understand if you need time, but I sincerely hope you can forgive me someday.</li>
<li>My deepest apologies for my behavior. I hope to regain your trust and love.</li>
<li>I'm so sorry for letting you down. I value your forgiveness above all else.</li>
<li>I am truly ashamed of my actions and regret them deeply.  I’ll work to earn back your trust.</li>
